QuestData.Title: Irondeep Supplies
QuestData.Description: Before the fighting started, we stored supplies for Dun Baldar in the Irondeep mine. The troggs that surfaced there weren't much of a problem when we had spare troops to guard the mine, but now that we're fighting with the Horde we can't maintain control of Irondeep.$B$BWe need the supplies in Irondeep, $n. Enter the mine and bring me a load of them.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring 10 Irondeep Supplies to the Alliance Quartermaster in Dun Baldar.
QuestData.CompletionText: Do you have the supplies, $N? We can never have enough!
QuestData.RewardText: Well done! I'll put these supplies to good use! Thanks, $N!
